    "training both modes (constant & xi) via `train_multi_bubble_on_dataset`,\n",
    "and testing in the static-condensation assembly.\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "## Colab setup\n",
    "Run this cell first if using Google Colab (otherwise skip it)."
